{"tid":1283233,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"死，唔係一個解決方法","createTime":"2019-07-03T17:57:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-03T18:51:18.000Z","uid":25663,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6b9281188aaad7775bec59de8262f19a663b5687","tid":1283233,"uid":25663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T17:57:33.000Z","msg":"死左之後，你愛嘅人，愛你嘅人都會為你傷心<br />\n<br />\n相反，你嘅敵人會得益<br />\n<br />\n先行一步只會打擊其他同路人<br />\n變相助長左其他唔同立場嘅人<br />\n<br />\n你諗下，連死你都唔怕，有咩阻到你？<br />\n<br />\n生存落去先有無限嘅可能<br />\n儘管未來係黑暗，有機會會失敗，但你會有千千萬萬個同伴陪住你失敗，我地可能贏唔到，但係我地可以一直輸落去，我地可以唔放棄未來，唔放棄戰友，唔放棄自己<br />\n<br />\n留住條命，留住個機會<br />\n話唔定係有生之年，我地可以一齊去到心目中嘅烏托邦呢？<br />\n<br />\n天佑香港，香港人先係令香港成為獨有存在嘅原因"},{"pid":"3c3c50db724c98c5fce45ece320878aeda1f92d6","tid":1283233,"uid":25663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T18:09:23.000Z","msg":"我無野講"},{"pid":"52486a27fb99e85a113f863e18056057403d8cd8","tid":1283233,"uid":25663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T18:09:47.000Z","msg":"我無野講"},{"pid":"0149b9422c450ee484b8272b25c25c6bab76f2dd","tid":1283233,"uid":25663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T18:09:57.000Z","msg":"我要搵律師"},{"pid":"fc56dccc96cf77a7ad9bd0250b4b8adea63e22dd","tid":1283233,"uid":25663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T18:10:12.000Z","msg":"我要飲水"},{"pid":"e83ffcce10d9072b7ffe9c2ace12d1f2fc76cffa","tid":1283233,"uid":25663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T18:10:23.000Z","msg":"我要去廁所"},{"pid":"3ef9d50f2e25d03fc1474efdfea31f6f8e3942c4","tid":1283233,"uid":25663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T18:10:40.000Z","msg":"我要大家齊齊整整"},{"pid":"e410bb0ac7721bc870cb7ef25d1e1f26262d31dc","tid":1283233,"uid":25663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T18:19:50.000Z","msg":"唔好先行一步，陪大隊行落去"},{"pid":"292594625b1ea1e21a55fe680316908216af49bd","tid":1283233,"uid":25663,"like"